snippet: A magnitude 6.0 quake hit in Oaxaca state in southwestern Mexico, the U.S. Geological Survey said on Sunday....

headline.print_headline: Magnitude 6.0 Quake Hits in Oaxaca, Mexico: USGS
headline.main: Magnitude 6.0 Quake Hits in Oaxaca, Mexico: USGS

lead_paragraph: A magnitude 6.0 quake hit in Oaxaca state in southwestern Mexico, the U.S. Geological Survey said on Sunday.
